  Reset E 1 13257 10 17
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13266
Name     &CThe Wild Shore - North&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The jungle thins out as you reach the western coastline. The ocean is
a brilliant, sparkling blue. However, the white sand is littered with
debris and the dangerous, slithering forms of Naga Explorers.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    13265
Desc      The Ruins of Zul'Mamwe.
~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    13267
Desc      The southern stretch of the shore.
~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     13267
Name     &CThe Wild Shore - South&d~
Sector   field~
Desc     The sandy beach continues southward. The wreckage of several merchant
